{"id":148039,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2011/04/简讯：中国要求超市购买滞销蔬菜/","date":"2011-04-27T08:30:24Z","modified":"2011-04-27T08:30:24Z","title":"简讯：中国要求超市购买滞销蔬菜","content":"<div>\n<p>中国商务部发布通知，要求各大型连锁超市购买河南、山东等地的滞销蔬菜。</p>\n<p>中国近日出现部分省份蔬菜收购价格低于成本，导致菜农损失惨重的问题。</p>\n<p>与此同时，城市居民却又面临蔬菜价格高的现象。</p>\n<p>商务部提出简化蔬菜进城环节，降低成本，保障市民和农民双方的利益。</p>\n</p></div>\n<div>\n<div>\n<p>\t<a href=\"http://www.bbc.co.uk/zhongwen/simp/china/2011/04/#page-top\" rel=\"nofollow\"><br />\n\t\t<span>点击</span><br />\n\t\t<span>页首</span><br />\n\t</a></div>\n</div>\n<p><a href=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/LybtQ-RXXIkbotUXRqZ81B--kBg/0/da\"><img border=\"0\" ismap src=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/LybtQ-RXXIkbotUXRqZ81B--kBg/0/di\"></a><br />\n<a href=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/LybtQ-RXXIkbotUXRqZ81B--kBg/1/da\"><img border=\"0\" ismap src=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/LybtQ-RXXIkbotUXRqZ81B--kBg/1/di\"></a></p>\n<p><img height=\"1\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/cnbbc/~4/gPqbZdmzNf8\" width=\"1\" /></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/f.fbz?AddNewUserDirect\">\n定期获得翻墙信息？<a href=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/?Sub=750556\">请电邮订阅数字时代</a> <br /><input name=\"EMAIL\" maxlength=\"64\" type=\"text\" size=\"25\" value=\"\"><br />\n<input name=\"FEEDID\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"750556\"><br />\n<input name=\"PUBLISHER\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"7485568\"><br />\n<input type=\"submit\" value=\"订阅!\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":176,"categories":[8779],"tags":[]}